'''耳垂'''（英文：Earlobe），是[[外耳|外耳]][[耳廓|耳廓]]的结构之一，由[[蜂窩組織|蜂窝组织]]、[[脂肪組織|脂肪组织]]构成，但缺乏耳廓其它部分所具有的韧性和弹性。<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Earlobe Rejuvenation|author=Hotta, Tracey|url=https://journals.lww.com/psnjournalonline/Citation/2011/01000/Earlobe_Rejuvenation.14.aspx|journal=Plastic Surgical Nursing|issue=1|year=2011|volume=31|page=39-40|access-date=2021-03-07|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315145537/https://journals.lww.com/psnjournalonline/Citation/2011/01000/Earlobe_Rejuvenation.14.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

